## Drag-and-Drop Install

1. Download the release zip.
2. Extract it.
3. Copy the included `ox_lib` folder into your server resources.
4. Replace your current `ox_lib` only after making a backup.
5. Keep the folder name as `ox_lib`.
6. Restart the resource:

```txt
restart ox_lib
```

## Server Config

Make sure `ox_lib` starts before resources that depend on it:

```txt
ensure ox_lib
ensure your_inventory
ensure your_clothing
ensure your_other_scripts
```

## Common Issues

### The UI did not change

Clear your FiveM cache and restart `ox_lib`.

### Test commands do not work

The test commands must be placed in a client-side resource. They will not work if pasted directly into F8.

### Some scripts still use their own UI

Only scripts using `ox_lib` UI modules will show this redesign. Custom UI from other resources will not be affected.
